snippet.textDisplay: I'm not a boomer or anything but just to let you know sonic and pacman were only like 10 years difference. I think that original gaming like Pacman and Sonic were very good though I have never played them because they pave the way for modern games. And plus they are a huge part of gaming culture and heritage. So while it's easy to make fun of pacman and stuff because it's "old" doesn't mean it's good and there are many games and many different kinds of gamers. Fortnite is not the only game and has really ruined gaming nowadays. Many people prefer playing older games and while they are not my cup of tea I basically don't think it's right to diss those games because they aren't Fortnite or anything. Not that there is anything wrong with Fortnite but Pacman and Sonic etc are on a way advanced level.
